An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
国内出现首例境外输入关联病例。
The first foreign-related imported cases occurred in China.
美国单日新增超过7000。
America adds more than 7,000 a day.
德国病死率不到0.4%文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑| 郝洲一、国内出现首例境外输入关联病例图1今日国内简述：截至3月20日24时，国内报告新增确诊病例46例，其中45例为境外输入。
Not more than 0.4% and # 124; Caijing's data researcher Xu Jintu & # 124; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & nbsp; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45
国内唯一1例本土新增病例来自广东省，系首例境外输入关联病例。
The only new case in China comes from Guangdong Province and is the first foreign-related imported case.
相关入境者于3月9日入境，目前共甄别20名密切接触者，已集中隔离观察。
The relevant entrants entered the country on 9 March, and a total of 20 close contacts have been screened and have been centralized for observation.
考虑到近来对入境者防控力度加大，普遍集中隔离14天，今后应可杜绝此类输入关联的本地传播。
In the light of the recent increase in immigration control and the widespread concentration of 14 days in isolation, it should be possible to eliminate the local transmission of such input links in the future.
武汉市及湖北省连续4日无新增确诊。
Wuhan and Hubei provinces did not have new diagnosis for 4 consecutive days.
北京市区级定点医疗机构将从3月23日起全面恢复日常医疗服务。
On March 23, designated medical institutions at the district level in Beijing will resume routine medical services.
湖北省早稻播种减少50万亩，中稻增加80万亩。
Early rice sowing decreased by 0.5 million mu and medium rice increased by 0.8 million mu in Hubei Province.
二、海外累计确诊超过20万，进入日增3万的轨道图2海外已经步入了日增3万的快速轨道，何时达到峰值尚未可知。
Cumulatively, more than 200,000 people have been diagnosed overseas, and a growing 30,000-strong track chart 2 Overseas has entered a fast-track orbit of an increasing 30,000. It is unclear when the peak will be reached.
新加坡从22日午夜起禁止所有短期旅客过境或入境该国。
Singapore has banned all short-term travellers from crossing or entering the country from midnight on the 22nd.
印度从22日起，每日早上7时至晚上9时实施宵禁，所有国民在这14小时内都不允许外出。
In India, a curfew has been in effect from 7 a.m. to 9 p.m. daily from 22 a.m. to 9 p.m. All nationals are not allowed to go outside during this 14-hour period.
图3日本和伊朗似乎有所抬头。
Figure 3: Japan and Iran seem to be on the rise.
尽管我们非常不希望看到，但从走势判断，意大利接下来很可能不会沿着桔色线（湖北）继续走，而是斜插向红线（美国）。
Although we do not want to see, but judging from the trend, Italy is not likely to continue along the orange line (Hubei), but to tilt to the red line (United States).
这意味着意大利的情况尚未缓解。
This means that the situation in Italy has not abated.
欧洲还在高速区间，明天就要超过中国一倍。
Europe is still in the high zone, and will surpass China by tomorrow.
美国还在全面赶超中，明天将穿过黄线，超过同时段的中国。
The United States is still in full catch-up and will cross the yellow line tomorrow, ahead of China at the same time.
我们的担忧丝毫不能减轻。
Our concerns cannot be alleviated in any way.
三、美国成功研发45分钟快速测试剂图4美国确诊病例迅速突破了2万，单日新增已是全球第一。
Diagram 4 The number of confirmed cases in the United States has soared to more than 20,000, making it the world's number one single-day addition.
纽约州成为美国第一个确诊人数破万的州。
New York State became the first state in the United States to have a confirmed count.
原因在于纽约州已经测试了超过45,000例疑似病例，测试量是加州等其他州的两倍之多。
That's because the state of New York has tested more than 45,000 suspected cases, twice as many as other states such as California.
美国食品及药物管理局（FDA）批准首只用于新冠病毒的快速测试剂，该试剂由加州分子医学分析公司赛飞（Cepheid）制造，大约45分钟内可以得知结果。
The Food and Drug Administration (FDA) approved the first rapid test agent for the new crown virus, manufactured by California molecular medicine analyst Cepheid, and the results are available in about 45 minutes.
白宫也确诊了首例病例，患者是美国副总统彭斯办公室的工作人员，彭斯夫妇也接受了病毒检测。
The first case was confirmed at the White House by a staff member from Vice President Burns's office, who were also tested for the virus.
彭斯的新闻秘书米勒（Katie Miller）21日晚在推特上发表声明称，副总统和妻子的新冠病毒检测呈阴性。
Burns's press secretary, Katie Miller, said in a Twitter statement late Thursday that the Vice President and his wife tested negative for the virus.
纽约市一监狱内一名犯人确诊新冠肺炎，这是美国联邦监狱首次出现犯人感染新冠病例。
A New Crown Pneumonia confirmed by a New York City inmate is the first new case of infection in a U. S. federal prison.
目前该犯人处于单独监禁，只有医护人员在对他进行例行检查。
The prisoner is currently in solitary confinement and is routinely examined only by medical personnel.
四、英国民众抢购10亿英镑食品，意大利全国停产图5英国首相约翰逊警告说，如果英国公众不听从政府建议留在家中的话，英国的国民保健服务（NHS）就有可能在两周内和意大利医疗系统一样，出现医院难以处理过多病人的危机。
British Prime Minister Lyndon Johnson warns that if the British public does not heed the government's advice to stay at home, the NHS could find it as difficult for hospitals to cope with a crisis of too many patients within two weeks as the Italian health system does.
NHS也史无前例地向私家医院临时聘用了2000名医护人员及征用了8000张病床，为接收可能会迅速增加的病人做好准备。
The NHS has also recruited an unprecedented 2,000 staff and 8,000 beds in private hospitals on an unprecedented basis to prepare for a potentially rapid increase in the number of patients.
过去三个星期来，英国公众在超市抢购囤积了价值10亿英镑的食品。
Over the past three weeks, the British public has been snapping up ￡1bn worth of food in supermarkets.
丹麦三个地区因缺乏检测设备已停止对新冠肺炎病毒检测。
Three regions of Denmark have stopped testing for the new crown pneumonia virus because of a lack of testing equipment.
中国援助塞尔维亚抗疫医疗专家组一行6人21日晚抵达贝尔格莱德，中方共向塞方捐赠16吨医疗物资，包括呼吸机、口罩、防护服等，将分两批送达塞尔维亚。
The Chinese side donated 16 tons of medical supplies, including respirators, masks and protective clothing, to Serbia in two batches.
此外，中国政府和民间各界捐赠的一批医疗物资, 包括医用口罩、防护服、护目镜、手套等，于21日空运抵达雅典国际机场。
In addition, a donation of medical materials, including medical masks, protective clothing, goggles and gloves, from the Chinese Government and the private sector arrived at Athens International Airport by air on 21 January.
图6当地时间21日晚，意大利总理孔特宣布，全国停止所有非必要的生产活动，在非必要情况下应实行远程办公。
Fig. 6 In the evening of the 21st local time, Italian Prime Minister Conte announced that all non-essential production activities would be halted nationwide and telecommuting would be introduced if necessary.
孔特称，意大利正面对二战以来最严峻的危机。
Conte said Italy was facing its worst crisis since World War II.
在疫情最严重的伦巴第大区，地区政府决定采取更严厉措施，即日禁止所有聚会，户外运动及练习亦被禁止。
In the Lombardy region, where the epidemic is most severe, the regional government has decided to take more severe measures, namely a daily ban on all gatherings and outdoor sports and practices.
同时要求所有在伦巴第的酒店顾客在72小时内离开。
At the same time, all hotel customers in Lombardy are required to leave within 72 hours.
意大利首家帐篷医院21日于克雷莫纳市正式启用，位于克雷莫纳市医院门前，由15个帐篷组成，投入使用后将能提供68张病床，其中包括8张重症护理病床。
Italy's first tent hospital, officially opened in the city of Cremona on 21 July, is located in front of the Cremona City Hospital and will consist of 15 tents, which, when operational, will provide 68 beds, including 8 for intensive care.
医院无需外部支援，完全独立运行，化验室、放射扫描、药房等各种仪器设施一应俱全。
The hospital is completely independent, without external support, and has a full range of facilities, including laboratories, radiography scans, pharmacies, etc.
图7德国累计确诊也超过2万，甚至超过了伊朗，但是德国的死亡率不到0.4%。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases in Germany also exceeds 20,000, or even Iran, but the German mortality rate is less than 0.4 per cent.
德国死亡率低的原因：1、德国很早得到预警，在新冠肺炎疫情到达欧洲之前几周便着手准备。
The reason for the low death rate in Germany: 1. Germany was warned early on to start preparing for the outbreak weeks before it reached Europe.
德国科研团队1月初便开发出快速检测试剂。
German research teams developed rapid detection reagents in early January.
2、德国在很早期便对疑似病例进行检测，发现患者。
2.Suspected cases are detected in Germany at an early stage.
这样做有助于为患者提供最优化的治疗，而不是在患者疾病恶化之后才提供治疗。
This helps to provide optimal treatment for the patient, rather than after the patient's illness worsens.
3、德国则有很多不同层级的实验室能够进行检测，每周最多可进行16万次新冠病毒检测。
3. In Germany, many different levels of laboratories are able to conduct tests, up to 160,000 new crown viruses per week.
4、德国相对于人口的医生数量、床位数和呼吸机数量在全球处于较高水平。
The number of doctors, beds and respirators in relation to the population in Germany is at a high global level.
据统计，德国有约2.8万个重症病房，配有2.5万台呼吸机。
According to statistics, there are about 28,000 intensive care units in Germany, with 25,000 ventilators.
图8今天小编终于推出了法国的疫情地图，原因在于法国的官方统计数字怎么加也跟总数对不上。
Fig. 8 The French epidemic map was finally released today because French official statistics do not match the total.
法国21日至少9座城市实施宵禁，违反宵禁的人员将会被处罚。
France 21 at least nine cities imposed a curfew, curfew violators will be punished.
法国卫生部长维兰这是一场“刚刚开始的长跑比赛”，这预示着法国目前暂定持续15天的“封城”措施实施期限很可能会延长。
French Health Minister Jean-Marie Whelan is in the early stages of a long-distance race, suggesting that France's current 15-day "closure" is likely to be extended.
全球最大奢侈品集团LVMH3月21日宣布，向中国购买4000万个口罩。
LVMH, the world's largest luxury goods group, announced on March 21 that it was buying 40 million masks from China.
第一批1000万个口罩会优先提供给当地的医护人员。
The first batch of 10 million masks will be given priority to local medical staff.
该公司旗下Parfums Christian Dior、Givenchy Parfums和Guerlain三家彩妆、香水制作的厂房已转为生产免洗洗手液，免费捐给法国卫生部门。
The company's Parfums Christian Dior, Givenchy Parfs and Guerlain factories have been converted to wash-free hand sanitizers, which are donated free of charge to the French health sector.
五、伊朗将购物商场改造成方舱医院图9目前伊朗政府正在将全国范围内占地面积最大的购物商场Iran Mall改造为方舱医院，以收治更多的新冠肺炎患者。
Iran Converts Shopping Mall into a Square Mall Hospital The Iranian government is converting Iran Mall, the largest shopping mall in the country, into a square-cabin hospital to treat more patients with new crown pneumonia.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】六、全球疫情数字速览：【发电量增长1%】3月份以来，我国发用电量明显回升。
According to the statistics above, before Feb. 28, the cut-off time is 17: 00 Beijing time, and from Feb. 28, data by Caijing daily according to open data, the deadline is 9: 00 a.m. Beijing time.
3月17日，全国全口径发电量179亿千瓦时，较2月底提高10.8%，较去年同期增长1%，日发电量实现今年春节以来首次正增长。
On March 17, 17.9 billion kilowatt-hours of electricity were generated nationwide, up 10.8 percent from the end of February and 1 percent from the same period last year.
今年前2个月，全国规模以上工业发电量同比下降8.2%。
In the first two months of this year, industrial power generation above the national scale fell 8.2 per cent year on year.
小结：保持多日的国内零本土新增记录，被输入病例的关联病例打破，再次撬动国人的神经。
Summary: Maintain a multi-day domestic zero new local record, was entered into the case of a broken correlation, once again pry the nation's nerves.
美国纽约州加大了检测范围，结果确诊数量迅速上升，这是一个危险的信号。
Increased testing in the state of New York, the United States, has led to a dangerous rise in the number of confirmed cases.
好在美国已经全方位调动起来，45分钟出结果的检测试剂已经可以投入使用。
Fortunately, the United States has mobilized the full range of 45 minutes to produce the results of the test reagent is ready to use.
德国得到中国分享的病毒基因组信息之后，迅速研发了检测试剂，并及早对轻症患者展开治疗，因此死亡率一直较低。
Having received information on the viral genome shared by China, Germany has rapidly developed detection reagents and provided early treatment for mild cases, resulting in a consistently low mortality rate.
如果中国的作业不好抄，抄一下德国的作业也是可以的。
If China's homework is not easy to copy, a copy of the German homework can also be.
